title: The Beatles Stereo USB iso
description:
This USB memory stick contains pictures, music and video. The Music is stored in two formats, high quality 44.1 kHz 24bit FLAC and 320 Kbps MP3.

There is a Readme file on the memory stick which tells you how to play the FLAC files if you fon't already have a FLAC capable media player.

The MP3s can be played with the included music player or copied to iTunes using the 'Copy to iTunes' button, found in the music section.

If you don't want the files to be copied to your hard disk when adding to iTunes, make sure you have the correct import settings in iTunes.

More details can be found in the Readme.


The contains all The Beatles Remastered Stereo CD's in FLAC and MP3, Mini Documentaries, and Artwork. (original demonoid torrent)
